data.description: Ranch-Style 3 Bedroom. 2 Bathroom Home on a 15,682 SF Lot with Double Door Entry leading to a Step Down Living Room featuring Wood Beamed Vaulted Ceiling, Nice Brick Wood Burning Fireplace and Built-In Glass Display Cabinet. A Spacious Kitchen with Eating Area, Pantry and Lots of Cabinet Space. An Open Floor Plan including Family Room, Dining Room Inside Laundry Room. The Master Bedroom includes a Large Walk-In Closet and Master Bathroom with Separate Vanity Area. Wood Laminate Flooring Throughout. Energy Star Efficient Air Conditioning and Heat. Big 2 Car Garage Attached Garage. And Room outside for RV Parking.
